      • getGameProfile

        private static GameProfile getGameProfile(MinecraftServer server,
                                          java.lang.String username)
        Get a GameProfile given the MinecraftServer and the player's username. The UUID of the GameProfile will not be null. If the server is offline, a UUID based on the hash of the username will be used.
